headline: Merit Medical (MMSI) Surges 8.3%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Merit Medical (MMSI) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
